  {% when 'bharela-ringana' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'Bharela ringana is my absolute favourite Gujarati dish and this one does not disappoint. The brinjals are soft inside, the stuffing has a perfect balance of peanut, sesame and spices.' %}
  {% when 'gujrati-dal' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'The perfect balance of sweet, sour and spicy — exactly how Gujarati dal should taste. The jaggery and tamarind combination is subtle and not overdone. Had it with rice and ghee. Pure comfort food.' %}
  {% when 'deshi-chana' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'The black chana are perfectly cooked — firm bite, not mushy. The masala is robust with whole spices and you can tell it has been slow-cooked. Had it with puris for Sunday breakfast. Loved it!' %}
  {% when 'kathiyawadi-kadhi' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'This kadhi has the bold, spicy Kathiyawadi character — not the mild sweet Gujarati version. The buttermilk base is thick and the ginger-chilli flavour is prominent. Had it with khichdi. Absolutely perfect.' %}
  {% when 'methi-papad' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'Methi papad is a very unique dish and this one has got it right. The slight bitterness of fenugreek is balanced by the tomato and spice tadka. Crispy texture even after heating. Loved it as a snack!' %}
  {% when 'mag' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'Light, wholesome and incredibly flavourful. The whole moong are cooked perfectly and the garlic-tomato masala is simple but delicious. This is now my regular Tuesday lunch. Ordered 8 pouches.' %}
  {% when 'vaghareli-khichdi' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'The ultimate comfort food done right. Soft, well-seasoned and the tadka of mustard, cumin and curry leaves is fragrant. I top it with a spoon of ghee and it is absolutely divine. My family s favourite.' %}
  {% when 'kaju-butter-masala' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'This is genuinely restaurant quality. The cashews are plump, the gravy is rich and creamy, and the spice balance is perfect. My husband thought I had ordered from a restaurant. Absolutely delicious with naan!' %}
  {% when 'paneer-tikka' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'The smoky tikka masala flavour is exactly what you get at a good restaurant. Paneer is soft and the capsicum gives a nice crunch. Heated in microwave for 3 minutes and it was perfect. Genuinely impressive.' %}
  {% when 'paneer-but-masala' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'This is my go-to paneer butter masala now. The gravy is silky smooth, mildly sweet and perfectly spiced. The paneer is soft and absorbs the sauce beautifully. Better than most restaurant versions I have tried!' %}
  {% when 'paneer-rajwadi' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'The royal spice blend in this paneer dish is something else entirely. You can taste the whole spices — cardamom, clove, cinnamon — in every bite. Richer and more aromatic than regular paneer dishes. Felt like a special occasion meal.' %}
  {% when 'mutter-paneer' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'The green peas are sweet and not overcooked — that is the mark of good mutter paneer. The tomato gravy is well-balanced and not too heavy. My kids had it with rice and finished everything. Will order again!' %}
  {% when 'punjabi-chhole' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'As a Punjabi I am very picky about my chole and this genuinely delivered. Dark gravy, bold spicing, proper use of dried mango powder — it has the authentic Punjabi character. Perfect with bhature or kulcha!' %}
  {% when 'dal-taraka' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'The smoky butter-ghee tadka is what makes this dal special. You can smell the cumin and garlic the moment you open the pouch. Tastes exactly like the dal tadka at a good dhaba. My office lunch staple now.' %}
  {% when 'pau-bhaji' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'Being from Mumbai I had high expectations and this pav bhaji met all of them. The bhaji is thick, buttery and has the right colour. The street-food style spice level is spot on. Just add butter and toasted pav — perfection!' %}
  {% when 'shahi-paneer' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'The saffron aroma when you open the pouch is something else. The gravy is rich, mildly sweet and has a beautiful golden colour. Paneer is soft and fresh-tasting. Genuinely shahi — worthy of a special occasion dinner.' %}
  {% when 'palak-paneer' %}{% assign rv1_text = 'The spinach is fresh-tasting and properly pureed — not stringy or overcooked. The paneer cubes are a good size and the ginger-garlic base is well-balanced. My daughter who usually avoids palak had two servings!' %}
