  {% when 'paneer-tikka' %}{% assign rv2_text = 'Bold, flavourful and the right amount of heat. The tomato-cream base is rich without being too heavy. Had it with tandoori roti and it was a full restaurant experience at home. Will definitely reorder!' %}
